## Titles

Carrera SÃ©ptima, Dictum Factum, In Times Not Long Past, Et cetera ad
infinitum, Telecaster MP and others are titles chosen to mark the memory
of who I was reading, what I was practising, when and where I was at
that particular moment in time. And why do it? To remember, simply not
forget those precious moments. Titles are like stamps on envelopes
symbolizing the way in which the activities came to me.
